{"tid":1550964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］天水圍俊宏軒有手足比狗上門捉咗！！","createTime":"2019-09-07T19:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:03:54.000Z","uid":227227,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"95cb1f645561255a0864f45869c38b8a0e942577","tid":1550964,"uid":227227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"代Post ！<br />\n時間：22:45<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/3mdnh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F3mdnh&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=5fe6986e\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/3mdnh</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係拍俊宏軒第五座有加拉左兩位手足嘅當事人。<br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友係關𨋢期間，<br />\n見到著住有狗捉住兩位笠住頭套嘅朋友。<br />\n咁佢即刻Whatsapp我講，<br />\n同落樓去問保安發生咩事有冇搜查令...<br />\n保安話警察做野唔使問啦，<br />\n我係附近搵到嗌緊口號嘅手足過去幫手，<br />\n之後一齊過左去，我就再追問保安搭左邊部𨋢，<br />\n佢又係重覆講個句唔好問啦，<br />\n隔左幾分鐘之後popo就拎住個袋(證物？)好快上左車。<br />\n對唔住，我做唔到d咩，<br />\n太突發同太少人。<br />\n<br />\n影左狗車車牌：SR5974 TE6472<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEqQkEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEqQkEm.jpg&h=f593ff48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eisbPxH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeisbPxH.jpg&h=87ddc70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuTVwL2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuTVwL2.jpg&h=73d2ae35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7Vpp53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7Vpp53.jpg&h=f6ceedaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30e2c032f72279088c586e1a6a65f67213e1cafe","tid":1550964,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:10:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e54507ad0d12893aa7763abe6fa80c084407586","tid":1550964,"uid":258566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00c2a6c684115198177ef15c65e75ae2bdc18883","tid":1550964,"uid":227227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"78af5dca5eac61f5f42a564849ba9ee31fc914a8","tid":1550964,"uid":5104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:31.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n保安廢架？dllm"},{"pid":"9315d55ec3e5d203169081c8be9e79c4db7951e5","tid":1550964,"uid":178658,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"屌個保安仲要講埋句咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da09641b5a43d88ceff72479e2227bf085929fbb","tid":1550964,"uid":42978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9315d55ec3e5d203169081c8be9e79c4db7951e5","tid":1550964,"uid":178658,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"屌個保安仲要講埋句咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:23:46.000Z","msg":"天水圍北, 仲要係食蕉, 9成9係新移民, 全部藍到仆街, 唔好對佢地有期望"},{"pid":"374f7a39ec0a0a7b949624fb2bf237103a268cac","tid":1550964,"uid":72030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite